{"article_id":"eIbfopFZZdYL8vbN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump ' s latest immigration proposal marks a retreat on three areas of policy","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"in what","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"the White House said","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"was a \" good faith \" effort","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"to try to break the gridlock","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"that for more than a decade has thwarted every effort","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"to strike a compromise on the thorny issue .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"In each of those areas","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"- the Obama-era DACA program , Temporary Protected Status and a new path for asylum for children in Central America -","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Mr. Trump had canceled the Obama administration ' s initiatives .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"On Saturday , he did an about-face","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"and proposed to restore each of those programs .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Going further ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"he offered approval","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"to write them into law ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"giving them a permanence","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Mr. Obama could never win from Congress during his tenure .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"In exchange , he is asking for $ 5.7 billion for his plans","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"to build a border wall","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"as well as changes","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"to make it easier to deport illegal immigrant families","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and cut down on abuses of the asylum system .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"He also proposed items","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"both sides generally agree on ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"such as more technology","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"to scan for drugs in vehicles at legal border crossings","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"and a boost in the number of immigration judges","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"to cut into the backlog of cases .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"\" Today represents a compromise offer , \"","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence told reporters in a briefing after the president ' s announcement .","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"The embrace of Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals is a major change .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"Just days ago , Mr. Trump said","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"he didn ' t want to do anything","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"until the Supreme Court had a chance","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"to decide on his 2017 attempt","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"to phase out the deportation amnesty","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"that is protecting about 700,000 \" Dreamers. \"","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"Lower courts have split on that phaseout ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"leaving its future unclear .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Mr. Trump proposed writing the DACA program into law for those","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"already using it ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"giving them a guaranteed three years of protections .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Mr. Pence said","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Trump has been \" persuaded","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"this is the right thing","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"to do , now . \"","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"On Temporary Protected Status , the Homeland Security Department has signaled an end to the protection for as many as 300,000 people , some","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"who have been protected for two decades by a program","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"that ,","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"as its name suggests ,","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"was supposed to be temporary .","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"The White House in immigration negotiations last year resisted adding protected status holders into any deal ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"but that resistance has dissipated .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Indeed , Temporary Protected Status was the issue","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"that sparked Mr. Trump ' s harsh comments about those countries last year","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"when Democrats say","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"he called Haiti and Central American nations \" s-hole \" countries .","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"Mr. Pence on Saturday said","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Mr. Trump readily embraced adding the protected status deal into his proposal this time .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"The Trump administration in 2017 also canceled the Obama administration ' s Central American Minor program ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"which was designed","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"to give children","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"looking to get asylum in the U.S.","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"a chance","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"to apply from their home countries","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"rather than make the dangerous trek north .","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"The program drew slim participation","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"and was nixed","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"- drawing serious criticism from Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"who said","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"the president was forcing people to take the dangerous journey .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Mr. Trump is proposing to restart the Central American Minor program , this time with the full protections of law rather than an executive action .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Democrats would prefer to look at a full pathway to citizenship for the 1.5 million people","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"who could qualify for DACA","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"and the hundreds of thousands under Temporary Protected Status .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"They also said","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s offer is disingenuous","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"because he put Dreamers and TPS recipients in danger .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"\" It was effectively saying ,","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"' Look ,","depth":16},{"id":80,"text":"I created a problem","depth":17},{"id":81,"text":"by taking away protections for Dreamers .","depth":17},{"id":82,"text":"I created another problem","depth":16},{"id":83,"text":"by taking away protections for refugees .","depth":16},{"id":84,"text":"I ' m willing to undo part of the damage temporarily","depth":16},{"id":85,"text":"that I have inflicted","depth":16},{"id":86,"text":"to get my wall , ' \"","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"Rep. Adam B. Schiff , California Democrat , said on CBS ' s \" Face the Nation \" program .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"\" Well , that ' s really not much of an offer .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"And it wasn ' t intended to be . \"","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"Mr. Trump has moderated his own request from an original plan for $ 18 billion","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"to construct 700 miles of border barriers","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"to the current proposals of $ 5.7 billion","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"to build 230 miles .","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"He also wants to make it easier to deport illegal immigrant families","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"by cutting down on abuses of the asylum system","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"- items","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"he has sought for two years .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"He has been stymied by Democrats","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"who say","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"illegal immigrants deserve a chance","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"to make claims in the U.S .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s deal also includes items","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"that both sides generally agree on ,","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"such as more technology","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"to scan for drugs in vehicles at legal border crossings","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"and a boost in the number of immigration judges","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"to cut into the backlog of cases .","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"The Senate ,","depth":4},{"id":109,"text":"led by Republicans ,","depth":4},{"id":110,"text":"is slated to vote on Mr. Trump ' s plans next week .","depth":3},{"id":111,"text":"But House Democrats are unlikely to go along .","depth":3},{"id":112,"text":"Speaker Nancy Pelosi , California Democrat , rejected the president ' s proposal .","depth":4},{"id":113,"text":"She said","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"she will have her chamber vote instead on those few areas of overall agreement such as the immigration judges and scanning technology .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":229,"left":222,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":204,"right":221,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":142,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":124,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":121,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":0,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":117,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":1,"right":116,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":116,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":4,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":122,"right":9,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":122,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":125,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":140,"left":129,"right":139,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":12,"right":128,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":126,"right":127,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":133,"ri